com.mumfrey.liteloader.client

Class CallbackProxyClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mumfrey.liteloader.client.CallbackProxyClient

  • public class CallbackProxyClient
extends java.lang.Object
    Proxy class which handles the redirected calls from the injected callbacks and routes them to the relevant liteloader handler classes. We do this rather than patching a bunch of bytecode into the packet classes themselves because this is easier to maintain.
    Author:
    Adam Mummery-Smith
